 How to use:
 Compile in the addon-modules folder with WhiteCore-Sim (like all other Optional-Modules)
 Run WhiteCore.exe, change to the sim (using change region) that you wish to generate terrain for.
 Type "generate fractal terrain" and it will walk you through it.